data.description: Welcome to Your New Home! This single-story, like-new 2022 residence offers an ideal layout for families. The rear of the house boasts a spacious owner's suite with a full bathroom and a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms share a full bathroom conveniently situated in between. As you step through the front door, you'll enter an open-concept space encompassing the family room, dining area, and kitchen. Don't miss the opportunity to see this fantastic home today! Plus, take advantage of our exclusive 1% closing cost offer when you choose our preferred lender.
